<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>A 股连续下跌筛选（Baostock 本地数据）</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f1419;
      --panel: #1a2332;
      --text: #e7ecf3;
      --muted: #9aa7b2;
      --accent: #5b8cff;
      --border: #2a3545;
      --down: #ff6b6b;
      /* 名称(含代码) | 收盘 | 连跌天 | 连跌总 | 近N日 | 操作 */
      --row-grid: minmax(7rem, 2.1fr) minmax(4rem, 0.52fr) minmax(2.75rem, 0.38fr) minmax(4.25rem, 0.52fr) minmax(4.25rem, 0.52fr) minmax(5rem, 0.72fr);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.5;
    }
    header {
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #15202b 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
    }
    h1 { margin: 0 0 0.35rem; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 650; }
    .meta { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
    main { padding: 1rem 1.25rem 2.5rem; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .report-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }

    .report-head {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: var(--row-grid);
      gap: 0.35rem 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.45rem 0.65rem;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .report-head .rh-hint { text-align: right; }

    details.stock-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: rgba(26, 35, 50, 0.35);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    details.stock-card:hover { border-color: #3d4f66; }

    details.stock-card > summary {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: var(--row-grid);
      gap: 0.35rem 0.5rem;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.65rem 0.75rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      /* 浅色色块：由行内 --streak-tint 提供 */
      background: var(--streak-tint, rgba(26, 35, 50, 0.25));
    }
    details.stock-card > summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    summary .name-line {
      font-weight: 600;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    summary .code-inline {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }
    summary .chev {
      text-align: right;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      user-select: none;
    }
    details.stock-card[open] summary .chev { color: var(--muted); }

    .num { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; text-align: right; }
    .pct { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; text-align: right; }
    .neg { color: var(--down); }

    .card-body {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0 0.75rem 0.85rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--panel);
    }
    .card-body-inner {
      overflow-x: auto;
      padding-top: 0.65rem;
    }
    .card-body table {
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 280px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 0.84rem;
    }
    .card-body th, .card-body td {
      padding: 0.4rem 0.5rem;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .card-body th {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .empty { color: var(--muted); padding: 2rem 0; text-align: center; }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .report-head { display: none; }
      details.stock-card > summary {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.45rem 0.85rem;
        align-items: baseline;
      }
      summary .name-line { width: 100%; white-space: normal; }
      summary .chev { width: 100%; text-align: left; margin-top: 0.15rem; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>连续下跌 ≥ {{ min_streak_days }} 天（截至最新本地数据）</h1>
    <div class="meta">
      生成时间：{{ generated_at }} · 配置的数据结束日：{{ data_end_date or "—" }} ·
      近一月口径：{{ lookback_trading_days }} 个交易日涨跌幅 · 已排除 ST 类证券
    </div>
  </header>
  <main>
    {% if rows|length == 0 %}
      <p class="empty">暂无符合条件的股票，或尚未运行同步脚本生成 <code>data/</code>。</p>
    {% else %}
      <div class="report-list" role="list">
        <div class="report-head" aria-hidden="true">
          <span>股票（含代码）</span>
          <span class="num">最新收盘</span>
          <span class="num">连跌天数</span>
          <span class="pct">连跌总跌幅</span>
          <span class="pct">近{{ lookback_trading_days }}日</span>
          <span class="rh-hint">明细</span>
        </div>
        {% for r in rows %}
        <details class="stock-card" role="listitem" style="--streak-tint: {{ r.streak_bg }};">
          <summary>
            <span class="name-line" title="{{ r.stock_title }}">{{ r.stock_name }}<span class="code-inline">（{{ r.code }}）</span></span>
            <span class="num cell-close">{{ "%.3f"|format(r.latest_close) }}</span>
            <span class="num cell-streak">{{ r.streak_days }}</span>
            <span class="pct neg cell-stpct">{{ "%.2f"|format(r.streak_total_pct) }}%</span>
            <span class="pct cell-month {% if r.month_20_pct is not none and r.month_20_pct < 0 %}neg{% endif %}">
              {% if r.month_20_pct is not none %}
                {{ "%.2f"|format(r.month_20_pct) }}%
              {% else %}
                —
              {% endif %}
            </span>
            <span class="chev">展开每日跌幅</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-body-inner">
              <table aria-label="{{ r.stock_title }} 连跌明细">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>日期</th>
                    <th class="num">收盘</th>
                    <th class="pct">当日涨跌幅</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  {% for d in r.details %}
                  <tr>
                    <td>{{ d.date }}</td>
                    <td class="num">{{ "%.3f"|format(d.close) }}</td>
                    <td class="pct {% if d.day_pct < 0 %}neg{% endif %}">{{ "%.2f"|format(d.day_pct) }}%</td>
                  </tr>
                  {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </main>
  <footer>
    数据来源于 Baostock；列表不含 ST 类证券。仅供学习研究，不构成投资建议。
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
